				The 4 items mentioned in the post above describe what are called focus items.  These items, when implemented, will allow magicians to summon stronger pets.  There are necromancer versions of these out there too but I don't remember what they look like.  The effect for necromancers will be the same supposedly... I don't know if shamans or enchanters will have similiar items but we can hope :)
