				Yes, this is a component to the Broom of Trilon, and a previous poster has already mentioned the other components needed to complete this quest.<BR>
<BR>
My comment here is regarding the comment that using this item prior to 34 is of no benefit is not entirely correct.  The big jump in the pets at and after 34 is definately noticable, but I seldom got a green con air pet while using this item.  (Like 1 in 15-20 at level 23, where they should have been like 3 out of 5...)<BR>
<BR>
So yes, there is a benefit in using the complete Broom prior to level 34.  :)<BR>
